<html>
  <head>
    <title>Minerva Course Content Update</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <table
      align="center"
      border="0"
      cellpadding="0"
      cellspacing="0"
      width="600"
    >
      {{> emailHeader }}
      <tr>
        <td bgcolor="#ffffff" style="padding: 40px 30px 40px 30px;">
          <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
            <tr>
              <td
                style="color: #555555; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 24px;"
              >
                Minerva Course Content Update
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td
                style="padding: 20px 0 30px 0; color: #555555; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;"
              >
                Dear
                {{participantName}},
                <br /><br />
                We are excited to inform you about an update to the course
                content for the
                {{courseName}}. The following changes have been made:
                <br /><br />
                <strong>Old Content:</strong>
                <ul>
                  <li>Topic: {{oldTopic}}</li>
                  <li>Description: {{oldDescription}}</li>
                </ul>
                <strong>New Content:</strong>
                <ul>
                  <li>Topic: {{newTopic}}</li>
                  <li>Description: {{newDescription}}</li>
                </ul>
                We believe that these updates will enhance your learning
                experience and provide you with even more valuable insights and
                knowledge in the program.
                <br /><br />
                If you have any questions or need further clarification
                regarding the updated content, please feel free to contact our
                training coordinator,
                {{coordinatorName}}, at
                {{coordinatorEmail}}
                or
                {{coordinatorPhone}}. They will be happy to assist you.
                <br /><br />
                We appreciate your enthusiasm and commitment to your learning
                journey. Thank you for being a part of the training program.
                <br /><br />
                Best regards,
                <br />
                The Minerva Team
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
      {{> emailFooter }}
    </table>
  </body>
</html>